        "Fat"
      ],
      "text": "Fat was a swordsman who served as Piandao's loyal yet disgruntled butler. A serious man, Fat did not find many things humorous. He prepared meals and beverages for Piandao and his students, whom he also assisted in training."
    },
    {
      "body": "Fat came to Piandao many years before ${link_0}'s visit and proved his worth by cooking him a delicious dinner. Piandao trained Fat in exchange for some good, home-cooked grub, and the two have been together at ${link_1} ever since.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Sokka",
          "key": "${link_0}",
          "target": {
            "external": false,
            "href": "/wiki/Sokka",
            "page": "Sokka"
          }
        },
        {
          "body": "Piandao's castle",
          "key": "${link_1}",
          "target": {
