      "text": "When Sokka and his friends were leaving, Fat stopped them just outside the castle gate, saying that Piandao had sent him a gift to remember him by. He handed Sokka a small sack, inside of which was a white lotus Pai Sho tile, and bowed respectfully before returning inside."
